<h1>Forestry</h1>

<ol type=1><p>

<li>Identify and name ten (10) kinds of timber trees or shrubs. Tell the importance and uses of each.<p>

<li>Collect and identify seeds of ten (10) different kinds of trees.<p>

<li>Name three minor forest products, and give the sources and uses of each.<p>

<li>Name two important enemies of the forest. Suggest remedies to combat or prevent damage caused by each of these enemies.<p>

<li>Enumerate some effects of kaingin, and what remedies should be done. Tell something about the law penalizing illegal kaingin.<p>

<li>Tell something about the work of the Bureau of Forest Development and what it is doing for the country.<p>

<li>Understand the meaning of forest conservation and how it may be achieved. Give the importance of conserving forests.<p>

<li>Write a 300-word essay on the importance of forests to wildlife, the people of the community, and to our country.</ol>



</span><p>    </td>
